{"tid":884863,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"食神知道，哭是沒有用的。","createTime":"2018-11-01T02:35:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-01T18:35:27.000Z","uid":206224,"like":34,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"bce8a77e89a98ff4ad73d21d760090771bddbb17","tid":884863,"uid":206224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T02:35:19.000Z","msg":"謝霆鋒為廚而生，所以34歲轉型，開始了自己的廚藝生涯。霆鋒拍第一部片子《12道鋒味》系列美食節目時，他和300多棵蔬菜打打殺殺，因為太過入戲，他不小心擦過刀鋒，手指尾立即受傷，血如泉湧。 <br />\n<br />\n導演立刻喊停，要送他去醫院。他知道，這一去醫院，勢必要換人，那他的「食神之路」也許從此就斷了。於是，34歲的他對導演說：「找來300多棵蔬菜不容易，耽誤一天就是好多錢，我能堅持。」於是，他將鐵粉直接灑在傷口上，再將保鮮袋包著手指，戴上勞工手套繼續拍攝。換了四個保鮮袋，倒出四袋血，戲拍完時，他幾乎暈倒。<br />\n<br />\n送到醫院，醫生說，再遲來一點，人就玩完了，而且，極有可能得到破傷風。在給他煎藥之前，醫生讓他簽生死狀。 在醫生給他煎藥時，謝霆鋒就那麼看著，不喊、不叫、不哭，沒有戴護目鏡，就那樣一煲一煲地煎著。一個34歲的廢中，知道自己面對的是怎樣的人生。他知道，哭是沒有用的。<br />\n<br />\n最後一煲藥，霆鋒對醫生說：「我來煎！」醫生看著他，他居然笑了︰「Sorry，太入戲了。」<br />\n<br />\n這句話多麼豪邁，在場的人震驚了。因為醫生說，如果熬不過去，他也只有四天的生命了，所以，他願意嘗試生命中不曾嘗試的痛，他要給自己煎一煲。<br />\n<br />\n從給自己煎藥那一天開始，他知道，所有的明天全要靠自己。後來，他一直努力，不停地鳩煎，終於成為麥當勞鋒味安格斯煎蛋肉醬飽首席大廚。"},{"pid":"63cdda50ea44811d7d1928256f3407b7ce6686f1","tid":884863,"uid":74778,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T02:37:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://dingyue.nosdn.127.net/0GW2uXWpBvHqkr8CNnBixezlohwQb2wt3dEgpACsJXPWn1479255502071.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.nosdn.127.net%2F0GW2uXWpBvHqkr8CNnBixezlohwQb2wt3dEgpACsJXPWn1479255502071.gif&h=aa3c73a1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"23ceba5be55c302fe3a2e7607e88698df8e5857c","tid":884863,"uid":187076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T02:38:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uGVsrfV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuGVsrfV.jpg&h=018662d7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"274b9e75ce0d2e98b23e0e1974c75847959df895","tid":884863,"uid":206224,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T02:40:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.epochtimes.com/assets/uploads/2017/02/1-59-450x336.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.epochtimes.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F02%2F1-59-450x336.jpg&h=6e04883d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港星謝霆鋒日前曬出刮痧照片，其手臂和胸膛滿是紅色刮痕，健康狀況引人擔憂，連主演的新片《決戰食神》首映禮也缺席。經紀人霍汶希透露，<span style=\"color: red;\">他患手筋膜發炎，每天吃兩排止痛藥，被醫生禁止入廚切菜，美食節目或喊卡。</span><br />\n<br />\n港媒報導，謝霆鋒特別喜歡下廚，除了建立屬於自己的食品品牌，還獲得「米芝蓮」（即米其林）百年以來頒發的首個「米芝蓮之友」稱號，但成功的背後付出了不少代價。日前他在臉書貼出刮痧致半身通紅的照片，還留言：「醫生說不能再長期在廚房了，但是如果要在短時間內學會煮好任何東西，可能這就是代價了&hellip;&hellip;刮痧。」其傷勢令人憂心。<br />\n<br />\n謝霆鋒主持美食節目《12道鋒味》已達三年，因下廚常常拋鍋子、把刀切菜，令手部嚴重勞損。近日去醫院看骨科，被醫生告誡短期內不能再進廚房。霍汶希透露：謝霆鋒「一天吃一二排止痛藥都沒辦法止痛，他很傷心」。<br />\n<br />\n因為被醫生禁止拿菜刀，他只好轉而研究美食。此外，原定四五月間要拍攝的美食節目將延期，去西班牙拍廣告的計劃或生變。外傳他受到好萊塢動作片邀約，也要看身體狀況再做決定。霍汶希感嘆：「<span style=\"color: red;\">霆鋒都說沒想到被打到飛起來都沒事，反而因為煮到出事。</span>」<br />\n<br />\n看到謝霆鋒的照片後，粉絲紛紛留言，勸他放下鍋子，重拾唱歌和彈吉他。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/17/2/12/n8803642.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.epochtimes.com%2Fb5%2F17%2F2%2F12%2Fn8803642.htm&d=b7DOn9OyI3Miq2JAdG7N8BOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=bac24852\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/17/2/12/n8803642.htm</a>"},{"pid":"8eeae508891e998de4e067d7025bf9bccbc6a811","tid":884863,"uid":74778,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T02:40:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kFfsrgs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkFfsrgs.png&h=be6094d5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ddc765d6be189db6ca1fb4137891c46911bc28b7","tid":884863,"uid":75156,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T02:45:14.000Z","msg":"鐵粉灑落傷口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？？？"},{"pid":"6168fcc7806831829ef3ac5ad0207a4b1cbbe678","tid":884863,"uid":206224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ddc765d6be189db6ca1fb4137891c46911bc28b7","tid":884863,"uid":75156,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T02:45:14.000Z","msg":"鐵粉灑落傷口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？？？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T05:54:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"646bc8b2ebd5a26d1acfe4ea1e7f04af3a6b60b8","tid":884863,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8eeae508891e998de4e067d7025bf9bccbc6a811","tid":884863,"uid":74778,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T02:40:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kFfsrgs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkFfsrgs.png&h=be6094d5&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T05:56:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db2cff43895017e848bb85486da9aff19ea81801","tid":884863,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T05:59:03.000Z","msg":"在醫生給他煎藥時，謝霆鋒就那麼看著，不喊、不叫、不哭，沒有戴護目鏡，就那樣一煲一煲地煎著。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b67433348a848d14795398ca9f4fd5d745da0dd4","tid":884863,"uid":74262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T06:59:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"addbb0b0839dbe2af671e3e503cd787ccd0bee3e","tid":884863,"uid":206224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b67433348a848d14795398ca9f4fd5d745da0dd4","tid":884863,"uid":74262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T06:59:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T08:26:09.000Z","msg":"親力親為煎每塊M記漢堡<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81a6125aec23af1f8040b85827c3fd733e6c6fff","tid":884863,"uid":206224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T10:21:38.000Z","msg":"<img